iya Riaz]]''' || style=\"text-align:center\"|{{flagicon|PAK}} || {{birth date and age|1992|9|24|df=y}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|medium]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2021 || style=\"text-align:right;\"| ||||Overseas\n|-\n! colspan=\"10\"  style=\"background:#dcdcdc; text-align:center;\"| All-rounders\n|-\n|52|| [[Challuru Prathyusha]] || style=\"text-align:center\"|{{flagicon|IND}} || {{birth date and age|1998|7|25|df=y}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[medium-fast]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2021 || style=\"text-align:right;\"| ||||\n|-\n|3|| '''[[Indu Barma]]''' || style=\"text-align:center\"|{{flagicon|NEP}} || {{birth date and age|1997|9|29|df=y}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|medium]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2021 || style=\"text-align:right;\"| || ||Overseas\n|-\n|6|| '''[[Deepti Sharma]]''' || style=\"text-align:center\"|{{flagicon|IND}} || {{birth date and age|1997|8|24|df=y}} || Left-handed || Right-arm [[off break]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2021 || style=\"text-align:right;\"| ||||\n|-\n|8|| [[Neelam Bisht]] || style=\"text-align:center\"|{{flagicon|IND}} || {{birth date and age|1996|6|5|df=y}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[off break]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2021 || style=\"text-align:right;\"| ||||\n|-\n|29|| '''[[Bhagavathi Yasha]]''' || style=\"text-align:center\"|{{flagicon|IND}} || {{birth date and age|1999|11|14|df=y}} || Left-handed || Left-arm [[fast bowling|fast]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2021 || style=\"text-align:right;\"| ||||Vice-captain/Wicket keeper\n|-\n|39|| '''[[Natalie Sciver]]''' || style=\"text-align:center\"|{{flagicon|ENG}} || {{birth date and age|1992|8|20|df=y}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[Fast bowling|medium]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2021 || style=\"text-align:right;\"| |||| Overseas\n|-\n|1|| '''[[Kuna Shaila]]''' || style=\"text-align:center\"|{{flagicon|IND}} || {{birth date and age|1997|8|25|df=y}} || Right-handed || Right-arm [[fast bowl