ire T. Hanrahan\n|Sergeant\n|New York City Police Department\n|August 28 2007\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/19960-sergeant-claire-t-hanrahan|title=Sergeant Claire T. Hanrahan|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Frank Macri\n|Officer\n|New York City Police Department\n|September 3 2007\n|<ref name=\"auto22\">{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/19455-police-officer-frank-macri|title=Police Officer Frank Macri|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref><ref name=\"nydailynews.com22\" /><ref name=\"Another of the Forgotten Victims22\">{{Cite web|url=http://nycpba.org/publications/mag-08-12/macri.html|title=Another of the Forgotten Victims|date=2009-01-31|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090131115921/http://nycpba.org/publications/mag-08-12/macri.html|archivedate=January 31, 2009|access-date=2016-11-16|url-status=dead|df=}}</ref>\n|-\n|William J. Holfester\n|Detective\n|New York City Police Department\n|January 22 2008\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/19958-detective-william-j-holfester|title=Detective William J. Holfester|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|John E. Goggin\n|Detective\n|New York City Police Department\n|May 6 2008\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/21238-detective-john-e-goggin|title=Detective John E. Goggin|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Gary Mausberg\n|Officer\n|New York City Police Department\n|October 8 2008\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/20437-police-officer-gary-mausberg|title=Police Officer Gary Mausberg|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Alex W. Baez\n|Sergeant\n|New York City Police Department\n|November 22 2008\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/20850-sergeant-alex-w-baez|title=Sergeant Alex W. Baez|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Vito Mauro\n|Officer\n|New York City Police Department\n|December 2 2008\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/20278-police-officer-vito-mauro|title=Police Officer Vito Mauro|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Richard Jakubowsky\n|Officer\n|New York City Police Department\n|June 7 2009\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/20853-police-officer-richard-jakubowsky|title=Police Officer Richard Jakubowsky|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Renee Dunbar\n|Officer\n|New York City Police Department\n|August 25 2009\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/20408-police-officer-renee-dunbar|title=Police Officer Renee Dunbar|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Donald G. Feser\n|Inspector\n|New York City Police Department\n|September 12 2009\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/20854-inspector-donald-g-feser|title=Inspector Donald G. Feser|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Corey J. Diaz\n|Detective\n|New York City Police Department\n|October 7 2009\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/20858-detective-corey-j-diaz|title=Detective Corey J. Diaz|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Robert C. Grossman\n|Officer\n|New York City Police Department\n|October 9 2009\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/20857-police-officer-robert-c-grossman|title=Police Officer Robert C. Grossman|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial Page (ODMP)|access-date=2016-11-16}}</ref>\n|-\n|Charles J. Clark\n|Sergeant\n|New York City Police Department\n|November 7 2009\n|<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.odmp.org/officer/21239-sergeant-charles-j-clark|title=Sergeant Charles J. Clark|newspaper=The Officer Down Memorial 